---
title: Cheesy Lamb Meatballs & Tomato Sauce with Cauli-Potato Mash & Garlic Veggies
description: The trick to keeping these lamb meatballs succulent and moist is a fabulous tomato sauce, and once you’ve mastered how to
perfectly balance the flavours in yours you’ll never look back.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
